<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-58-0189 </DOCNO><TEXT>Topics discussed are autonomous vehicle guidance, three-dimensional systems,the Mars rover, motion analysis, and planning and navigation. Particularpapers are presented on a real-time system architecture for a mobilerobot, distributed scene analysis for autonomous road vehicle guidance,the vision system for a Mars rover, the recovery of motion parametersusing optical flow, and Prolog-based world models for mobile robot navigation.</TEXT></DOC>